18#ifndef GCC_INCPATH_H
19#define GCC_INCPATH_H
20
21extern void split_quote_chain (void);
22extern void add_path (char *, int, int, bool);
23extern void register_include_chains (cpp_reader *, const char *,
24 const char *, const char *,
25 int, int, int);
26extern void add_cpp_dir_path (struct cpp_dir *, int);
27extern struct cpp_dir *get_added_cpp_dirs (int);
28
29struct target_c_incpath_s {
30 /* Do extra includes processing. STDINC is false iff -nostdinc was given. */
31 void (*extra_pre_includes) (const char *, const char *, int);
32 void (*extra_includes) (const char *, const char *, int);
33};
34
35extern struct target_c_incpath_s target_c_incpath;
36
37enum { QUOTE = 0, BRACKET, SYSTEM, AFTER };
